BE CAREFUL!!!

I am changing a lot this project, is far from being stable.

The main components

Hardware:

MSP430 Launchpad from Texas Instruments, the transmitter

http://processors.wiki.ti.com/index.php/MSP430_LaunchPad_%28MSP-EXP430G2%29

Arduino, the receiver/gateway

http://www.arduino.cc/

APC220 the transceiver from Appcon 

http://www.appcon.com.cn/en/product/220_pro.html


Arduino ethernet shield ENC28J60
http://www.nuelectronics.com/estore/index.php?main_page=project_eth


Linux Debian, the mqtt server and the final application
http://www.debian.org/
http://mosquitto.org/documentation/python/


References:


RemoteSensor - Wireless Data Acquisition
http://www.obdev.at/products/vusb/remotesensor.html



AVR ethernet / web server
http://tuxgraphics.org/electronics/


